Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: triple seven radio
des: Listen to the latest from 777 ROCKIN RADIO . You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". This skill was created by RobinLynnes Productions for I Am Streaming.
